dc_title_s: Map of a portion of the Pymatuning Creek Basin and Yankee Creek Basin showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water|Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.|Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Pymatuning Creek Basin and Yankee Creek Basin and quality of underground water.|Scale bar lower right corner of map.
